ul.li:
Inline JavaScript or CSS
            Content:
JavaScript:<script type="text/javascript">
    /* Include JavaScript code here. */

    function myFunction() {
      return true;
    }
</script> 
CSS:<style>
    /* Include CSS style rules here. */

    *{
      color:red
    } 
</style>If
            you have special characters (&, <, etc.) that
            breaks the well-formedness of the XML fragment, it is important to place this content
            inside an XML
            comment:<script type="text/javascript">
  <!--
    /* Include JavaScript code here. */

    function myFunction() {
      return true;
    }
  --/>
</script>
